description: Number of point labeled reduced 5-free two-graphs with n nodes.
links: P. J. Cameron, Counting two-graphs related to trees, Elec. J. Combin., Vol. 2, #R4.
formula: E.g.f.: -2*LambertW(-1/2*exp(-1/2)*(1+x)^(1/2))/(1+x). - _Vladeta Jovovic_, Aug 21 2006a(n) ~ sqrt(2)*sqrt(4-exp(1)) * n^(n-1) / (8*exp(n-1)*(4*exp(-1)-1)^n). - _Vaclav Kotesovec_, Sep 30 2013
author: _Peter J. Cameron_
